    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a vibrant, deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with premium leather upholstery that remains soft and supportive, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a strict regimen of synthetic oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride without any unusual noises. This car has been garage-kept and comes with a comprehensive folder of service records, two sets of keys, and a set of all-weather floor mats. It is a dependable, well-cared-for example ready for its next owner to drive home with total confidence.",
      "price": 32000.0,
